'''无症状'''（英文：Asymptomatic），是指患者經檢測發現患有[[疾病|疾病]]但未体现出[[症状|症状]]，或只是该病[[病原体|病原体]]的[[帶原者|帶原者]]，或者已康复<ref>{{Cite web|title=Asymptomatic|url=https://medlineplus.gov/ency/article/002217.htm|accessdate=2020-12-30|author=|date=|format=|work=|publisher=[[美国国家医学图书馆|美国国家医学图书馆]]（U.S. National Library of Medicine）|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210319013609/https://medlineplus.gov/ency/article/002217.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite journal|title=Subclinical infection and asymptomatic carriage of gastrointestinal zoonoses: occupational exposure, environmental pathways, and the anonymous spread of disease|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23659675/|last=Quilliam|first=R. S.|last2=Cross|first2=P.|date=2013-10|journal=Epidemiology and Infection|issue=10|doi=10.1017/S0950268813001131|volume=141|pages=2011–2021|issn=1469-4409|pmid=23659675|last3=Williams|first3=A. Prysor|last4=Edwards-Jones|first4=G.|last5=Salmon|first5=R. L.|last6=Rigby|first6=D.|last7=Chalmers|first7=R. M.|last8=Thomas|first8=D. Rh|last9=Jones|first9=D. L.|access-date=2020-12-30|archive-date=2021-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210814071229/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23659675/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Definition of ASYMPTOMATIC|url=https://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/asymptomatic|accessdate=2020-12-30|author=|date=|format=|work=|publisher=[[梅里厄姆-韦伯斯特|梅里厄姆-韦伯斯特]]|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128141843/https://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/asymptomatic|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 如果该疾病是[[传染病|传染病]]，'''无症状感染'''（Asymptomatic infection）有时被称为“[[亞臨床感染|亞臨床感染]]”，但后者也可用于表示病患表现出了疾病的部分症状（而非全部）、还需进一步临床确诊<ref name=":0" />。 值得注意的是，如果病人在无症状的[[疾病潜伏期|潜伏期]]之后出现了症状，则症状出现之前的时期常被称为“症状前（pre-symptomatic）”<ref>{{Cite web|title=Coronavirus disease (COVID-19): How is it transmitted?|url=https://www.who.int/news-room/q-a-detail/coronavirus-disease-covid-19-how-is-it-transmitted|accessdate=2020-12-30|author=|date=|format=|work=|publisher=[[世界卫生组织|世界卫生组织]]（WHO）|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201015230546/https://www.who.int/news-room/q-a-detail/coronavirus-disease-covid-19-how-is-it-transmitted|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Definition of PRESYMPTOMATIC|url=https://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/presymptomatic|accessdate=2020-12-30|author=|date=|format=|work=|publisher=[[梅里厄姆-韦伯斯特|梅里厄姆-韦伯斯特]]|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210306205111/https://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/presymptomatic|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=新冠初期的人类困惑：传染是在无症状期？症状前？还是少症状时？|url=https://news.sina.cn/gj/2020-07-01/detail-iircuyvk1408183.d.html|accessdate=2020-12-30|author=|date=2020-07-01|last=|format=|work=|publisher=[[红星新闻|红星新闻]]|agency=[[新浪|新浪]]|language=zh|archive-date=2021-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210814071241/https://news.sina.cn/gj/2020-07-01/detail-iircuyvk1408183.d.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

部分无症状患者可以传播疾病。譬如，有研究指出[[2019冠状病毒病|2019冠状病毒病]]（COVID-19）患者中有40%-45%为无症状感染者，但无症状患者传播的风险低于有症状患者<ref>{{Cite journal|title=What the data say about asymptomatic COVID infections|author=Bianca Nogrady|url=https://www.nature.com/articles/d41586-020-03141-3|date=2020-11-18|journal=《[[自然_(期刊)|自然]]》（''Nature''）|issue=7835|doi=10.1038/d41586-020-03141-3|others=|year=2020|volume=587|page=|pages=534–535|language=en|pmid=|access-date=2020-12-30|archive-date=2021-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210316100110/https://www.nature.com/articles/d41586-020-03141-3|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Asymptomatic transmission of covid-19|url=https://www.bmj.com/content/371/bmj.m4851|last=Pollock|first=Allyson M.|last2=Lancaster|first2=James|date=2020-12-21|journal=BMJ|doi=10.1136/bmj.m4851|volume=371|language=en|issn=1756-1833|access-date=2020-12-30|archive-date=2021-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210325035808/https://www.bmj.com/content/371/bmj.m4851|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Prevalence of Asymptomatic SARS-CoV-2 Infection|url=https://www.acpjournals.org/doi/10.7326/M20-3012|last=Oran|first=Daniel P.|last2=Topol|first2=Eric J.|date=2020-06-03|journal=Annals of Internal Medicine|issue=5|doi=10.7326/M20-3012|volume=173|pages=362–367|issn=0003-4819|pmc=PMC7281624|pmid=32491919|access-date=2020-12-30|archive-date=2021-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121042535/https://www.acpjournals.org/doi/10.7326/M20-3012|dead-url=no}}</ref>。多數被認定為無症狀的COVID-19患者，屬於前症狀者（pre-symptomatic）<ref>{{Cite web|title=無症狀感染者真的無症狀？一表了解新冠肺炎無症狀、輕症、重症 {{!}} 預防自保 {{!}} 新冠肺炎|url=https://health.udn.com/health/story/120952/5484304|access-date=2021-05-31|last=聯合新聞網|work=元氣網|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2021-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210814082146/https://health.udn.com/health/story/120952/5484304|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

